Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "aws_cloudtrail" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name           = "<example_resource_name>"
  s3_bucket_name = "<example_resource_name>"
  enable_logging = true

  insight_selector {
    insight_type = "ApiCallRateInsight"  # Critical fix: enables CloudTrail Insights on the trail
  }
}
```
